{"title":"FaceTiming on your Apple TV 4K? You don’t have to hold your iPhone anymore","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2254848/facetime-belkin-phone-mount-with-magsafe-for-apple-tv-4k.html","date":1709583215000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>With tvOS 17, Apple added the ability to make <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/1942675/you-can-now-take-facetime-calls-on-your-apple-tv-4k.html\">FaceTime calls with the Apple TV 4K</a>. Since the Apple TV 4K doesn’t have a camera, Apple implemented Continuity Camera, which allows the Apple TV 4K to connect to an iPhone and use its camera. That, however, introduced a new problem: what do you do with the iPhone when making a FaceTime call on Apple TV 4K? Prop it up under your TV against a book? Awkwardly hold it in your hand while looking at your TV? Use some two-sided tape and stick your iPhone on the wall above the TV?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thankfully, Belkin released a solution to this first-world problem. The new iPhone Mount with MagSafe for Apple TV 4K allows you to put the iPhone in a proper place elegantly. Compatible with the iPhone 12 or later, the mount can be placed atop your TV, or if your TV is sitting on a table or entertainment center, it can sit below it. It can also be mounted on a wall.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The mount offers a tilt range of -20 to +30 degrees and can hold the iPhone in either portrait or landscape mode. The mount is made of finished metal and includes a two-year warranty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Priced at $49.99/£49.95, Belkin is currently taking pre-orders for the <a href=\"https://www.belkin.com/iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-apple-tv-4k/P-MMA010.html\">iPhone Mount with MagSafe for Apple TV 4K</a>, with shipping slated for later this month. (U.K. readers can order from the <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=1-1-2254848-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/uk/shop/product/HR1V2ZM/A/belkin-iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-apple-tv-4k\">Apple Store U.K.</a>) Belkin also makes the <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.belkin.com/iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-mac-desktops-and-displays/MMA007btGY.html&amp;xcust=1-1-2254848-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">iPhone Mount with MagSafe for Mac Desktops and Displays</a> ($39.99 at the <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=1-1-2254848-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HQ652ZM/A/belkin-iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-mac-desktops-and-displays\">Apple Store</a>) and the <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.belkin.com/iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-mac-notebooks/MMA006btBK.html&amp;xcust=1-1-2254848-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">iPhone Mount with MagSafe for Mac Notebooks</a> ($29.99 at the <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=1-1-2254848-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HQ642ZM/A/belkin-iphone-mount-with-magsafe-for-mac-notebooks\">Apple Store</a> or on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Belkin-MagSafe-MacBook-Continuity-Compatible/dp/B0BJNHF6WJ/?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">Amazon</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>See the slideshow below for the different configurations of the iPhone Mount for Apple TV 4K.</p>\n\n\n\n<div><div><ul><li><figure><img alt=\"Belkin  iPhone Mount for Apple TV 4K\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/belkin-continuity-camera-tv-stand.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></li><li><figure><img alt=\"Belkin  iPhone Mount for Apple TV 4K\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/belkin-continuity-camera-tv-wall-mount.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></li><li><figure><img alt=\"Belkin  iPhone Mount for Apple TV 4K\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/belkin-continuity